This is a simple package for post-processing of data from LAMMPS.

Now it contains the following parts:

- AveTime.py
- AveChunk.py
- GreenKubo.py
- FileOperation.py
- MDData.py
- utils.py

## Install
You can install this package using pip.
```shell
pip install PostMD
```
